  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's a desktop shortcut labeled \"start\"... you click it and a popup appears. Let the loop begin.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing gameplay:</strong> loot currency to farm, buy upgrades to get stronger</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced progression:</strong> unlock new upgrades every minute</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Theory-crafting:</strong> optimize your upgrade tree to clear the bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Low stakes:</strong> reset your upgrades at any time if you're stuck</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377410/extras/d3c2677a6b7cd1e3c4ae504c4d3d0fc6.poster.avif?t=1742633630\" width=580 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377410/extras/d3c2677a6b7cd1e3c4ae504c4d3d0fc6.webm?t=1742633630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377410/extras/d3c2677a6b7cd1e3c4ae504c4d3d0fc6.mp4?t=1742633630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 125 unique upgrades to unlock. Experiment with different builds and find the right combination to clear the game!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's a desktop shortcut labeled \"start\"... you click it and a popup appears. Let the loop begin.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing gameplay:</strong> loot currency to farm, buy upgrades to get stronger</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-paced progression:</strong> unlock new upgrades every minute</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Theory-crafting:</strong> optimize your upgrade tree to clear the bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Low stakes:</strong> reset your upgrades at any time if you're stuck</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377410/extras/d3c2677a6b7cd1e3c4ae504c4d3d0fc6.poster.avif?t=1742633630\" width=580 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377410/extras/d3c2677a6b7cd1e3c4ae504c4d3d0fc6.webm?t=1742633630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377410/extras/d3c2677a6b7cd1e3c4ae504c4d3d0fc6.mp4?t=1742633630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 125 unique upgrades to unlock. Experiment with different builds and find the right combination to clear the game!</p>",
